      "title": "Introduction to Be Verb",
      "order": 1,
      "duration": 10,
      "content": "Be Verb English की सबसे fundamental verb है। इसकी 5 forms हैं: am, is, are, was, were। हर English sentence में कहीं न कहीं be verb होती है। इसे सही तरीके से use करना English का पहला step है।\n\nBe Verb के 2 tenses हैं:\n1. Present: am, is, are\n2. Past: was, were\n\nBe Verb के uses:\n- Identity: I am Rahul.\n- Description: She is beautiful.\n- Location: He is at home.\n- Occupation: They are engineers.\n- State/Condition: We are tired.",
      "keyPoints": [
